Package: vineyard
Architecture: all
Depends: wine, icoutils, cabextract, unzip, python-glade2, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Provides: wine-preferences, nautilus-wine, python-wine
Replaces: wine-preferences, nautilus-wine, python-wine
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Description: Easy to use Wine configuration program
 Vineyard is a user friendly configuration tool for Wine that offers all the
 features of winecfg (with the exception of the unfinished theme-support) as
 well as bottle-handling and program-management in an easy to use program
 designed to blend in with the GNOME desktop.
